      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.On2ZrPJTe8FURsXY]{Operative Exploit}</p>\n<p>You exploit elevation to deliver especially deadly attacks from afar. When performing a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.MBNI94tbMoqizPUk]{Trick Attack (Ex)} with a sniper weapon, and so long as you’re at least 20 feet above your target for every 100 feet between you and the target (minimum 20 feet), you gain a bonus to the attack’s damage equal to half your operative level. You must have the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.KHg9HjJVua1BA6ti]{Debilitating Sniper (Ex)} exploit to learn this exploit.</p>"
